      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STANDPOINT (1) last appeared two months ago over 1811m at this track when he fell. This is his first run for the Juan Arriagada stable. Plenty to like about his prospects. FINAL DRAMA (2) went forward and gave a great sight before finishing second last time out over 1710m at Tampa Bay Downs (Dirt). Should settle handy in the run. It doesn't get any easier but on his best form he is good enough to take this out. DENYING (5) missed the frame on dirt over 1646m at Tampa Bay Downs two back then filled a minor placing last start on the same surface at Tampa Bay Downs, beaten 0.3 lengths over the 1646m journey. Going well at present and is sure to be thereabouts. SYNTACTIC (10) missed the placings two runs back then didn't do any better last start when 15 lengths away in 11th over 1710m at Tampa Bay Downs. Best efforts measure up so worth another chance.",
